example.programlisting:
curl -i -d \
'{
    "loadBalancer": {
        "name": "a-new-loadbalancer",
        "port": 80,
        "protocol": "HTTP",
        "virtualIps": [
            {
                "type": "PUBLIC"
            }
         ],
        "nodes": [
            {
                "address": "<IP address of FIRST cloud server>",
                "port": 80,
                "condition": "ENABLED"
            }
        ]
    }
}' \
-H 'X-Auth-Token: your_auth_token' \
-H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
'https://dfw.loadbalancers.api.rackspacecloud.com/v1.0/your_acct_id/loadbalancers'

curl -i -d \
'{
    "nodes": [
        {
            "address": "<IP address of SECOND cloud server>",
            "port": 80,
            "condition": "ENABLED"
        }
    ]
}' \
-H 'X-Auth-Token: your_auth_token' \
-H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
'https://dfw.loadbalancers.api.rackspacecloud.com/v1.0/your_acct_id/loadbalancers/load_balancer_id/nodes'
